{"tid":1405311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦嚴厲譴責極端激進分子侮辱國旗　挑戰國家主權","createTime":"2019-08-04T08:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T09:07:43.000Z","uid":41404,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"53533d22e71b0a8c6e1647eb263bdf046a58a5f6","tid":1405311,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:58:39.000Z","msg":"中聯辦負責人發聲明，嚴厲譴責香港極端激進分子侮辱國旗、挑戰國家主權的違法行徑。<br />\n<br />\n負責人表示，昨日下午香港有喪心病狂的極端激進分子，在尖沙咀扯下某建築前懸掛的中華人民共和國國旗並扔入海中，這是繼7月21日激進示威者圍攻中聯辦、污損國徽後對國家尊嚴的又一次公開挑釁。<br />\n<br />\n負責人又說，國家主權和尊嚴不容挑戰，「一國兩制」原則底線不容觸碰，包括廣大香港同胞在內的全體中國人的愛國情感，不容肆意傷害；必須依法嚴懲這種無法無天的惡行，重申堅定支持特區政府和警方嚴正執法，依法懲治暴力犯罪分子，維護香港法治和社會穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472456-20190804.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472456-20190804.htm&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUBz2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=3689c4fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472456-20190804.htm&h=b594f1f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472456-20190804.htm</a>"},{"pid":"02